tostellar\naccretion phases, increasing rapidly up to 65 degree at the onset of radiation\npressure feedback.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 16 Sep 2016 20:00:00 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-11-23"}
